description:
Questionnaires used to collect the ETMED-L project's data.   
 More details regarding the project are available in its published protocol: Berney A, Carrard V, Berney S, Schlegel K, Gaume J, Gholam M, et al. Study protocol for the ETMED-L project: Longitudinal study of mental health and interpersonal competence of medical students in a Swiss university using a comprehensive framework of empathy. BMJ Open. 2021;11:e053070. doi:&nbsp; 10.1136/bmjopen-2021-053070  
